rted to an executable output type\n\nNow I'm updating the project file to target .NET 8.0 and adjusting the package references accordingly. , but in v3 the runner is built into the executable itself, so this configuration might not be necessary anymore. Let me think through whether the global.json needs updating or if it can be removed entirely.\n\nBefore I proceed with the migration, I should check what .NET SDKs are currently available on the system.","outputTokens":1291,"requestId":"E3C0:2CBD0C:19A15C8:1C9F1E4:6A052BE3"},"id":"6962eefd-38b1-4580-9cc9-52639bd7aa28","timestamp":"2026-05-14T01:57:15.761Z","parentId":"5e80b2cc-c814-4dcf-91cd-1f21d2c3d6a8"}
